   5:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @brief   TIM HAL module driver.
   6:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *          This file provides firmware functions to manage the following
   7:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *          functionalities of the Timer Extended peripheral:
   8:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *           + Time Hall Sensor Interface Initialization
   9:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *           + Time Hall Sensor Interface Start
  10:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *           + Time Complementary signal break and dead time configuration
  11:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *           + Time Master and Slave synchronization configuration
  12:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *           + Timer remapping capabilities configuration
  13:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   @verbatim
  14:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   ==============================================================================
  15:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****                       ##### TIMER Extended features #####
  16:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   ==============================================================================
  17:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   [..]
  18:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     The Timer Extended features include:
  19:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     (#) Complementary outputs with programmable dead-time for :
  20:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****         (++) Output Compare
  21:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****         (++) PWM generation (Edge and Center-aligned Mode)
  22:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****         (++) One-pulse mode output
  23:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     (#) Synchronization circuit to control the timer with external signals and to
  24:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****         interconnect several timers together.
  25:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     (#) Break input to put the timer output signals in reset state or in a known state.
  26:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     (#) Supports incremental (quadrature) encoder and hall-sensor circuitry for
  27:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****         positioning purposes
  28:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c **** 
  29:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****             ##### How to use this driver #####
  30:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   ==============================================================================
